simpledb.remote
Class StatementAdapter

java.lang.Object
  simpledb.remote.StatementAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.sql.Statement, java.sql.Wrapper
Direct Known Subclasses:
SimpleStatement
public abstract class StatementAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.sql.Statement

This class implements all of the methods of the Statement interface, by throwing an exception for each one. Subclasses (such as SimpleStatement) can override those methods that it want to implement.

Author:
Edward Sciore
